course_description: In this course, students will expand knowledge of commonly diagnosed health disorders of infants, children and adolescents in ambulatory settings, acute care clinics or the emergency room.
prerequisites: NRSG 757D and NRSG 758D or equivalent transfer credit as prerequisites.
